data.description: Newer home in West Greeley backs to open space, walking trail and park! Open floor plan with 10ft ceilings, kitchen has breakfast bar and opens to the dining room and both the living room & great room. Main floor master bdrm (3/4 bath), laundry room and 1/4 guest bath. Upstairs are 2 bdrms and a full bath. Room to grown in the large, unfinished walkout basement. Sprinkler systems front and back and a partial vinyl fence. OS 2-car garage. Windsor school district and easy access to I-25.
